Sangmin completed his PhD at the SCSI lab (<a href="http://www.yonsei.ac.kr/en_sc/">Yonsei University</a>) in Korea. 
The topic of his PhD was â€œDesign and Implementation of 3D Underground Cadastral System in Koreaâ€. 
His research interests are in database modeling and 3D building modelling with focus on the real-world implementation of 3D land administration and cadastral system.</p>

